{
  "dataList": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "content": "<color=purple>我是多么热切渴望</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "content": "<color=purple>更为幸福、明朗的未来</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "content": "<color=purple>而我站在此处，在这门前</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "content": "<color=purple>令人留恋的往昔啊</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "content": "<color=purple>我已下定决心</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "content": "<color=purple>你因我的怒火遭受过多少苦痛</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "content": "<color=purple>粗鲁而笨拙的沉着</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "content": "你忽视了多少自身的奇迹",
      "vocalid": 1
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "content": "率直而诚实的态度",
      "vocalid": 1
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "content": "<color=purple>在你我二人伫立的命运之丘</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "content": "<color=purple>我将了结一切</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "content": "<color=purple>你是否会见证我的结局？</color>",
      "vocalid": 1
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "content": "<color=purple>哦</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "content": "<color=purple>我们转啊转</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "content": "<color=purple>怀抱着苦痛</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "content": "<color=purple>受自我驱使</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "content": "<color=purple>藏匿着感情</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "content": "<color=purple>彼此的记忆相互交织</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "content": "<color=purple>而你将永远不会知晓</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "content": "<color=purple>但我知晓</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "content": "<color=purple>一切错在于我</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "content": "<color=purple>使你不再露出笑容</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "content": "<color=purple>剥夺了你眼中的希望</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "content": "<color=purple>一切错在于我</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "content": "<color=purple>你所倾吐的谎言</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "content": "<color=purple>但愿即使我不在身旁，你也能获得幸福</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "content": "<color=purple>这是通过丛丛盛放的紫色花朵们流传至今的信息</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "content": "<color=purple>不论我们多么相悖</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "content": "<color=purple>早安</color>",
      "vocalid": 0
